# CODEX HANDOFF PROMPT — Wildlife Crime Intelligence Platform

You are continuing implementation work on a **Wildlife Crime Intelligence Platform** — a production-grade, AI-powered system that monitors Indian wildlife crime news in 13 languages, classifies incidents using NLP, and provides a real-time intelligence dashboard.

